Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,世界在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不可杀人 不可偷盗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不可欺瞒 不可奸淫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都是谎言 诓骗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不想被杀 不想被盗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才以正义伦理等谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,保护弱小的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,原始的真理乃是弱肉强食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,吞噬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,人的财富 权力 乃至世界本身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有我布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,能击碎世界的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,带来真实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All Hail Britannia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}All Hail Britannia
